WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.790
Hey, good morning family. How are y'all

00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:05.269
doing today? Well, praise the Lord. We

00:00:05.279 --> 00:00:07.909
have another video for you.

00:00:07.919 --> 00:00:09.750
I was praying last

00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:11.509
night and seeking the Lord, and he's

00:00:11.519 --> 00:00:13.110
talking to me a lot about things that

00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:16.390
are coming, things for my future,

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:19.750
for my kids, and for what he has for us.

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:21.910
But a lot of you—I've noticed some of

00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:23.750
the emails say, "Oh, Brother

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:25.189
Brandon, none of that's going to happen

00:00:25.199 --> 00:00:26.630
when we're here. We're going to be taken

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:29.029
in the rapture before. We won't see any

00:00:29.039 --> 00:00:31.750
of that stuff."And I have to say, you're

00:00:31.760 --> 00:00:35.190
delusional. None of

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:37.590
the other prophets are prophesying that.

00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:39.110
None of the other ministers are

00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:42.549
ministering that. What

00:00:42.559 --> 00:00:44.150
makes you think that God's only going to

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:47.350
tell you this stuff? I

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:49.910
have no idea why I'm the only one the

00:00:49.920 --> 00:00:51.750
Lord tells. He said, "Brandon, because

00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:53.029
I'm going to tell you, I have a lot of

00:00:53.039 --> 00:00:56.389
people try to be my

00:00:56.389 --> 00:00:56.399
friend."And

00:00:56.399 --> 00:01:01.029
you go, "Okay, can I talk

00:01:01.039 --> 00:01:02.869
to them? Can I hang out with

00:01:02.869 --> 00:01:02.879
them?"And

00:01:02.879 --> 00:01:05.670
the Lord says, "No, I've called you to

00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:07.990
be separate unto me. You won't have

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.390
friends in this because they will

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:12.950
influence the way I talk to you because

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:14.630
their opinions don't line up with what

00:01:14.640 --> 00:01:18.149
I'm saying."That's interesting because

00:01:18.159 --> 00:01:19.990
I will reach out and want to talk to

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.030
people and the Lord said, "That's the

00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:22.950
last conversation. Don't continue

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:24.870
to do that.

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:27.429
Don't do that because their opinions

00:01:27.439 --> 00:01:29.429
don't line up with what I'm

00:01:29.439 --> 00:01:31.030
telling you, Brandon. I'm trying

00:01:31.040 --> 00:01:32.950
to lead you in a direction and warn

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:35.350
my people what's coming."Now, what

00:01:35.360 --> 00:01:37.429
they're hearing, that's between them and

00:01:37.439 --> 00:01:39.190
God. I'm not here to judge that. I'm

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:40.870
here to follow what the Holy Spirit

00:01:40.870 --> 00:01:40.880
tells

00:01:40.880 --> 00:01:43.510
me to tell you. And if it witnesses with

00:01:43.520 --> 00:01:46.310
you and it bears witness in your spirit,

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:48.149
then go by it. If it doesn't, put it on

00:01:48.159 --> 00:01:49.749
the shelf. But at least I can say I told

00:01:49.759 --> 00:01:52.710
you so. The Lord told me, he said,

00:01:52.720 --> 00:01:54.069
"There's a difference,

00:01:54.069 --> 00:01:54.079
Brandon."He

00:01:54.079 --> 00:01:55.670
said so many people say, "Lord, all

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:56.950
these people say you're

00:01:56.950 --> 00:01:56.960
humble."Even

00:01:56.960 --> 00:01:59.429
big

00:01:59.439 --> 00:02:01.749
ministries say, "Oh, you're

00:02:03.759 --> 00:02:05.510
humble."And

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:09.749
he said, "Brandon, humility

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:12.710
is something of the heart. Either

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:15.430
you have it or you don't. Either you

00:02:15.440 --> 00:02:18.869
recognize that it's Christ in you or you

00:02:18.879 --> 00:02:21.830
don't. It's

00:02:21.840 --> 00:02:24.390
black and

00:02:24.390 --> 00:02:24.400
white."And

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:26.229
I can tell you, ladies and gentlemen,

00:02:26.239 --> 00:02:29.030
if you really knew how my education was

00:02:29.040 --> 00:02:31.990
and who I really am as a person,

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:34.710
I am—in

00:02:34.710 --> 00:02:34.720
the natural—what

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:37.030
I perceive is a very insecure

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:40.229
person a lot of times about things. But

00:02:40.239 --> 00:02:41.750
the Lord told me, he said, "Brandon, I've

00:02:41.760 --> 00:02:44.470
called you to be secure in me. It doesn't

00:02:44.480 --> 00:02:47.270
matter what men say about

00:02:47.270 --> 00:02:47.280
you."And

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:50.710
he has me on a path to tell you all

00:02:50.720 --> 00:02:53.990
what he says, and I stand with him

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:56.229
regardless of what

00:02:56.239 --> 00:02:58.309
everybody else says—how popular you can

00:02:58.319 --> 00:03:00.630
be or who invites you to their house or

00:03:00.640 --> 00:03:03.670
their conference or whatever. I

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:07.030
don't care. I prefer really to stay

00:03:07.040 --> 00:03:09.589
right here in my garden praying and

00:03:09.599 --> 00:03:11.430
talking to the Father and looking at my

00:03:11.440 --> 00:03:12.949
flowers.

00:03:12.959 --> 00:03:15.430
I don't care about all that other stuff.

00:03:15.440 --> 00:03:18.070
This is just me. I'm real. All that

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:20.309
other crap doesn't matter.

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:22.309
People try to boost up an ego real

00:03:22.319 --> 00:03:24.949
quick. I see a lot of ego

00:03:24.959 --> 00:03:26.470
in the body of Christ in the

00:03:26.480 --> 00:03:28.309
upper leadership. A lot of people with

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:30.869
big heads that feel they're like

00:03:30.879 --> 00:03:32.949
Saul. You know what it's like? It's like

00:03:32.959 --> 00:03:35.830
Saul whenever he lost the

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:39.110
anointing; David had it and he

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:41.270
thought he was still called of God and

00:03:41.280 --> 00:03:42.550
God was still speaking to him. They

00:03:42.550 --> 00:03:42.560
are

00:03:42.560 --> 00:03:46.070
as dry as a desert spiritually

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:47.910
and they're still pretending that they've got

00:03:47.920 --> 00:03:50.390
it and they don't have it anymore. I've

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:53.430
seen it a lot and they walk around with

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:55.509
this big puffed-up ego and spiritual

00:03:55.519 --> 00:03:57.830
head thinking the

00:03:57.840 --> 00:03:59.270
Lord's still talking to them and they

00:03:59.280 --> 00:04:01.429
haven't had a fresh word in years.

00:04:01.439 --> 00:04:03.509
They're still running off of

00:04:03.509 --> 00:04:03.519
twenty-year

00:04:03.519 --> 00:04:06.229
revelation. But God is a now God and he

00:04:06.239 --> 00:04:08.470
speaks fresh revelation all the time.

00:04:12.159 --> 00:04:14.789
I've tried to

00:04:14.799 --> 00:04:17.509
tell you all the people that you see

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:20.949
in the forefront now

00:04:20.959 --> 00:04:23.350
won't be there soon. And you'll see a

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:25.749
new generation of Davids rising up

00:04:25.759 --> 00:04:28.310
beyond anybody's comprehension of what's

00:04:28.320 --> 00:04:30.629
about to take place. But it's not to

00:04:30.639 --> 00:04:33.510
glorify man. It's to glorify God. And

00:04:33.520 --> 00:04:37.590
it's about him getting the glory.

00:04:37.600 --> 00:04:41.270
Ego and resume, ego and platform is no

00:04:41.280 --> 00:04:44.550
more. It's all about Jesus. And I'm

00:04:44.560 --> 00:04:46.870
telling you, to get the work done that

00:04:46.880 --> 00:04:49.909
he wants done, you're going to see the

00:04:49.919 --> 00:04:52.070
glory move in services that you had no

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:53.909
idea he'd move into. You think he'd be

00:04:53.919 --> 00:04:57.510
in some big shot's service, but

00:04:57.520 --> 00:04:59.189
you'll hear that the glory showed up in

00:04:59.199 --> 00:05:01.110
a nobody's service in the natural. Do

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:03.030
you know what I'm saying? Just because

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:04.710
Jesus could move through them because

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:07.510
they didn't have a puffed-up head. Their

00:05:07.520 --> 00:05:10.390
head was deflated. It was just because

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:13.029
they were hungry. For "blessed are those

00:05:13.039 --> 00:05:14.230
that hunger and thirst after

00:05:14.240 --> 00:05:18.390
righteousness, for they will be

00:05:18.390 --> 00:05:18.400
filled."So

00:05:18.400 --> 00:05:21.430
that's what I had to say. And

00:05:21.440 --> 00:05:23.749
then there's a lot of you who get mad about

00:05:23.759 --> 00:05:26.629
big preachers having a lot of money. And

00:05:26.639 --> 00:05:29.110
I heard you all say certain ministers,

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:30.870
"Oh, they're the devil. They have this,

00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:33.749
they have that."And as a

00:05:33.759 --> 00:05:37.270
person who cleaned for big ministries

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:39.590
most of his life, yeah, it's

00:05:39.600 --> 00:05:41.749
frustrating. You see they have

00:05:41.759 --> 00:05:43.110
multi-million dollar homes,

00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:45.270
multi-million dollar furniture, flying

00:05:45.280 --> 00:05:47.670
around in multi-million dollar planes,

00:05:47.680 --> 00:05:50.150
private airplanes, private islands,

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:52.629
going out and doing stuff. And the Lord

00:05:52.639 --> 00:05:55.189
blessed them. And you'd see a lot of the

00:05:55.199 --> 00:05:56.870
lay people in the body of Christ,

00:05:56.880 --> 00:05:58.629
they would do without. You see a lot of

00:05:58.639 --> 00:06:01.670
them working for nothing

00:06:01.670 --> 00:06:01.680
and

00:06:01.680 --> 00:06:03.990
they're sowing.

00:06:03.990 --> 00:06:04.000
They're sowing

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:07.350
hard. They give hard. And

00:06:07.360 --> 00:06:12.629
I believe there is a balance of

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:14.550
things that the Lord wants to get across

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:17.189
with people because you've been burnt

00:06:17.199 --> 00:06:19.189
and you give up on things. Well, I don't

00:06:19.199 --> 00:06:20.469
believe God wants us blessed,

00:06:20.479 --> 00:06:21.990
and then you start talking bad

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:24.150
about the man of God.

00:06:24.160 --> 00:06:27.590
I learned this:

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:30.070
no matter how blessed I saw them, I

00:06:30.080 --> 00:06:32.390
would look at what they gave. I would

00:06:32.400 --> 00:06:35.510
look at how they gave. I would look at

00:06:35.520 --> 00:06:38.150
their lifestyle of how they would help

00:06:38.160 --> 00:06:41.749
other people. And the Bible says that if

00:06:41.759 --> 00:06:43.350
you give, it shall be given unto

00:06:43.350 --> 00:06:43.360
you—good

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:44.710
measure, pressed down, shaken

00:06:44.720 --> 00:06:46.469
together, and running over will men

00:06:46.479 --> 00:06:49.830
give into your bosom.

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:51.749
But if you are not in ministry and you

00:06:51.759 --> 00:06:53.590
don't have those huge platforms whenever

00:06:53.600 --> 00:06:55.270
people aren't giving those multi-million

00:06:55.280 --> 00:06:57.350
dollar checks to you, how do you make

00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:58.950
it?

00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:01.189
Because my mom and dad, we were

00:07:01.199 --> 00:07:03.350
all grunts in the ministry. All of us

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:05.909
were. And they struggled. I mean, I

00:07:05.919 --> 00:07:08.870
live on food stamps. And you go, "Man, we

00:07:08.880 --> 00:07:10.469
believe in God just to get through."And

00:07:10.469 --> 00:07:10.479
we're

00:07:10.479 --> 00:07:13.029
always looking for that

00:07:13.039 --> 00:07:15.510
Holy Ghost

00:07:15.510 --> 00:07:15.520
handshake—the

00:07:15.520 --> 00:07:18.150
gifts and surprises in the mail. A

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:20.309
lot of times they never come. You would sow and

00:07:20.309 --> 00:07:20.319
sow and

00:07:20.319 --> 00:07:22.469
believe

00:07:22.479 --> 00:07:25.990
God. But I got a hold of

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:28.230
the scripture that he gives you power to

00:07:28.240 --> 00:07:31.430
get wealth, that he anoints your hand to

00:07:31.440 --> 00:07:34.469
do something. And I got to the

00:07:34.479 --> 00:07:37.430
point where I started

00:07:37.430 --> 00:07:37.440
realizing—I'd

00:07:37.440 --> 00:07:40.870
watch how the world

00:07:40.880 --> 00:07:44.469
had ideas and the millionaires

00:07:44.479 --> 00:07:48.070
had ideas to get wealth through

00:07:48.080 --> 00:07:50.550
jobs and businesses and things

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:53.670
like that, but they weren't janitors,

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:55.990
but they set up

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:57.749
side hustles. They would do

00:07:57.759 --> 00:08:00.550
real estate, they would do stocks

00:08:00.560 --> 00:08:04.390
or whatever. So I sow my seed and I

00:08:04.400 --> 00:08:07.189
start asking God for wisdom. Asking the

00:08:07.199 --> 00:08:10.469
Father, "Show me how to become the head

00:08:10.479 --> 00:08:12.469
and not the tail."And I'm telling you,

00:08:12.479 --> 00:08:15.350
working a Monday through Friday, 8 to 5

00:08:15.360 --> 00:08:17.909
job, making minimum wage, you're

00:08:17.919 --> 00:08:20.070
never going to do it. You're going to

00:08:20.080 --> 00:08:22.469
have to believe God for a creative idea

00:08:22.479 --> 00:08:25.110
to get wealth. I would say in the

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:27.670
natural it's to own your own business, to

00:08:27.680 --> 00:08:31.350
have a company, to create. Ask God for

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:34.870
what you're good at. Do something that

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:38.070
God has anointed you to do.

00:08:38.080 --> 00:08:40.149
I've said this before, ladies

00:08:40.159 --> 00:08:42.310
and gentlemen, but it's the truth. You

00:08:42.320 --> 00:08:46.070
never see people working at Lowe's or

00:08:46.080 --> 00:08:49.030
Home Depot 8 to 5, Monday through Friday,

00:08:49.040 --> 00:08:50.630
just believing they'll get into upper

00:08:50.640 --> 00:08:54.389
management and become wealthy.

00:08:54.399 --> 00:08:55.990
We just made a good living,

00:08:55.990 --> 00:08:56.000
but

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:57.990
you struggled. You have your

00:08:58.000 --> 00:08:59.430
little house and your little

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:01.910
car, and we're satisfied. We're happy.

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:03.750
But the Lord wants you to have above

00:09:05.440 --> 00:09:07.190
and beyond all that you dare ask

00:09:07.200 --> 00:09:10.230
or think. God is a blessed God. And they

00:09:10.240 --> 00:09:11.350
said, 'Well, you're a prosperity

00:09:11.350 --> 00:09:11.360
preacher.'You're

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:14.150
right. You're right, I

00:09:14.160 --> 00:09:15.829
am. I want to see the body of Christ not

00:09:15.839 --> 00:09:18.389
struggle because I was there. I

00:09:18.399 --> 00:09:20.310
remember. Then the Lord gave me

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:23.990
ideas to start detailing cars. I

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:26.470
started detailing cars because I worked

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:28.710
for a mega-ministry, and they taught me

00:09:28.720 --> 00:09:30.710
how to detail cars. They taught me

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:32.310
how to extract carpets. I cleaned

00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:35.110
airplanes. I did things for them; I

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:37.430
learned how to do things, wax

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:40.949
stuff, clean, and get stains out.

00:09:40.959 --> 00:09:42.790
I learned all that. So, I took

00:09:42.800 --> 00:09:44.389
the knowledge that I had from doing

00:09:44.399 --> 00:09:47.190
that, and I created a business. I

00:09:47.200 --> 00:09:49.509
started detailing cars on the side, and

00:09:49.519 --> 00:09:51.910
I'd clean five extra cars. I'd work my

00:09:51.920 --> 00:09:55.110
tail end off. On the

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:57.269
weekends, I only took off on Sundays to

00:09:57.279 --> 00:09:59.590
go to church because I had

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:01.509
to work that afternoon at

00:10:01.519 --> 00:10:03.430
the church to shut it down, and

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:05.750
I'd go out and do all day Saturday. So,

00:10:05.760 --> 00:10:08.230
I worked sometimes seven days a week

00:10:08.240 --> 00:10:10.389
until I built up enough money and we put

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:13.110
it back. We struggled, but it took

00:10:13.120 --> 00:10:15.269
time. I would sow, and

00:10:15.269 --> 00:10:15.279
I believed

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:16.870
God. I would detail those

00:10:16.880 --> 00:10:18.870
cars and find people in the

00:10:18.880 --> 00:10:21.030
church and hand out flyers, whatever

00:10:21.040 --> 00:10:22.790
it took, saying, 'Hey, listen. I've got a

00:10:22.800 --> 00:10:24.310
detail business.'And they would say,

00:10:24.320 --> 00:10:25.829
'Oh, yeah, Brandon,

00:10:25.829 --> 00:10:25.839
whatever.'I'd

00:10:25.839 --> 00:10:28.230
charge a hundred bucks. A hundred bucks! Man,

00:10:28.240 --> 00:10:29.590
I was so excited to get that hundred

00:10:29.600 --> 00:10:32.150
bucks. I took that $100 and I

00:10:32.160 --> 00:10:34.150
would sow my 10% and take a little

00:10:34.160 --> 00:10:36.150
extra and believe God. If I could get

00:10:36.150 --> 00:10:36.160
an

00:10:36.160 --> 00:10:39.190
extra four cars on a Saturday, I'd

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:41.590
work all day long for $400. I

00:10:41.600 --> 00:10:43.509
thought that was amazing because I worked

00:10:43.519 --> 00:10:44.949
hard for it. After supplies and

00:10:44.959 --> 00:10:46.790
everything, it wasn't that much

00:10:46.790 --> 00:10:46.800
because

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:48.630
I had to buy my supplies.

00:10:48.640 --> 00:10:51.030
It was a lot, but I

00:10:51.040 --> 00:10:53.269
just kept going, building it,

00:10:53.279 --> 00:10:54.790
and working

00:10:54.800 --> 00:10:56.949
year after year.

00:10:56.959 --> 00:10:58.630
I kept building my clientele up,

00:10:58.640 --> 00:11:00.630
and then the Lord said, 'I

00:11:00.640 --> 00:11:02.150
want you to do something else.'So, I

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:04.870
got some dogs and started

00:11:04.870 --> 00:11:04.880
raising

00:11:04.880 --> 00:11:08.069
champion

00:11:08.079 --> 00:11:10.550
bloodline dogs

00:11:10.560 --> 00:11:14.790
for

00:11:14.800 --> 00:11:17.509
special needs

00:11:17.509 --> 00:11:17.519
kids—companion

00:11:17.519 --> 00:11:20.790
dogs for therapy. You

00:11:20.800 --> 00:11:22.310
know, when my daughter got diagnosed

00:11:22.320 --> 00:11:24.710
with autism, a therapy dog was really

00:11:24.720 --> 00:11:27.110
good for her. So, I started having ideas

00:11:27.120 --> 00:11:29.190
of how to help out therapy kids and

00:11:29.200 --> 00:11:31.030
making money doing that. What I'm

00:11:31.040 --> 00:11:33.269
trying to say is then Diana had the idea

00:11:33.279 --> 00:11:34.870
for eBay, and everybody knows we've done

00:11:34.880 --> 00:11:36.790
eBay and Poshmark, and that's what we do.

00:11:36.800 --> 00:11:38.949
So, instead of getting frustrated with

00:11:38.959 --> 00:11:42.389
people and seeing their blessing, look

00:11:42.399 --> 00:11:46.230
at the seed they sowed and then believe

00:11:46.240 --> 00:11:48.710
God for your idea.

00:11:48.720 --> 00:11:52.310
Believe God. When you sow your seed, you

00:11:52.320 --> 00:11:54.790
start sowing into good ground. And

00:11:54.800 --> 00:11:57.269
that's whenever I started realizing that

00:11:57.279 --> 00:12:00.230
not all ground was created equal in the

00:12:00.240 --> 00:12:03.110
eyes of the Lord.

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:05.030
People got mad at me when I started

00:12:05.040 --> 00:12:06.310
saying this kind of stuff. They get

00:12:06.320 --> 00:12:07.990
irritated because pastors don't like you

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:09.190
to say that kind of stuff. They get

00:12:09.200 --> 00:12:11.509
frustrated because they

00:12:11.519 --> 00:12:13.590
don't want you to try to hamper

00:12:13.600 --> 00:12:15.350
their churches or whatever.

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:17.110
I'm not trying to cause any ripples or

00:12:17.110 --> 00:12:17.120
waves;

00:12:17.120 --> 00:12:19.910
I just state what I feel and what

00:12:19.920 --> 00:12:23.750
the Lord shows me. So,

00:12:23.760 --> 00:12:25.829
over the course of time, the Lord has

00:12:25.839 --> 00:12:27.350
anointed me to do more and more.

00:12:27.360 --> 00:12:31.430
I want you to understand:

00:12:31.440 --> 00:12:33.910
God wants you blessed. God wants you

00:12:33.920 --> 00:12:35.590
prosperous. God wants you to have more

00:12:35.600 --> 00:12:37.829
than enough. I bring all this up because

00:12:37.839 --> 00:12:39.509
I know there's a lot of you that

00:12:39.519 --> 00:12:41.030
struggle.

00:12:41.040 --> 00:12:43.509
I try not to touch on

00:12:43.519 --> 00:12:45.590
finances very much because people get

00:12:45.600 --> 00:12:47.829
really annoyed when you talk about

00:12:47.839 --> 00:12:50.310
finances, especially in the body

00:12:50.320 --> 00:12:52.710
of Christ, because it seems that you

00:12:52.720 --> 00:12:55.509
all feel that it's been abused and

00:12:55.519 --> 00:12:59.190
I get a lot of hate from it. So I

00:12:59.200 --> 00:13:02.310
try to help you if you will listen,

00:13:02.320 --> 00:13:04.150
because I've been around the biggest of

00:13:04.160 --> 00:13:06.550
the biggest in the natural and I've

00:13:06.560 --> 00:13:09.829
watched it. I've watched how

00:13:09.839 --> 00:13:12.470
they

00:13:12.470 --> 00:13:12.480
sow.

00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:15.509
I've learned from some

00:13:15.519 --> 00:13:17.430
of the biggest names in ministry there

00:13:17.430 --> 00:13:17.440
are.

00:13:17.440 --> 00:13:20.710
The Lord has allowed me to

00:13:20.720 --> 00:13:23.030
see it. I've seen what they have,

00:13:23.040 --> 00:13:25.190
what they wear, and their

00:13:25.200 --> 00:13:27.910
closets. I've seen what the Lord's done

00:13:27.920 --> 00:13:30.710
with their lives. People criticize

00:13:30.720 --> 00:13:33.829
it, but I've seen what they give

00:13:33.829 --> 00:13:33.839
and

00:13:33.839 --> 00:13:36.389
how they sow. People go,

00:13:36.399 --> 00:13:39.750
'Well, you know,'whatever, man.

00:13:39.760 --> 00:13:41.829
I'm going to be honest with you: I could care

00:13:41.839 --> 00:13:45.509
less what they have

00:13:45.519 --> 00:13:48.629
if their ground is good.

00:13:48.639 --> 00:13:51.269
If their ground is good and it produces

00:13:51.279 --> 00:13:53.350
and you sow into it—say they had a

00:13:53.360 --> 00:13:55.910
billion dollars

00:13:55.920 --> 00:13:58.389
and their ground is good. You don't know

00:13:58.399 --> 00:14:01.829
what it takes to make ground good.

00:14:01.839 --> 00:14:03.990
What makes 100-fold ground, and what

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:06.949
sacrifice does it take to have 100-fold

00:14:06.959 --> 00:14:10.230
ground soil? Instead of criticizing them

00:14:10.230 --> 00:14:10.240
because

00:14:10.240 --> 00:14:13.189
they are blessed, look at their

00:14:13.199 --> 00:14:14.949
soil.

00:14:14.959 --> 00:14:18.069
Do they have good soil? Is their soil

00:14:18.079 --> 00:14:21.750
producing a 100-fold? Yes. Then there

00:14:21.750 --> 00:14:21.760
are

00:14:21.760 --> 00:14:23.670
not very many that do. So don't

00:14:23.680 --> 00:14:25.910
criticize it. Just sow into it and

00:14:25.920 --> 00:14:29.670
reap the fruit off of it. Don't be dumb,

00:14:29.680 --> 00:14:31.350
because what you talk against,

00:14:31.360 --> 00:14:34.629
you're not going to receive from.

00:14:34.639 --> 00:14:36.629
You've got to not talk against them

00:14:36.639 --> 00:14:39.189
because if you do, you don't receive the

00:14:39.199 --> 00:14:40.550
harvest off of it.

00:14:40.560 --> 00:14:43.750
I've learned: don't

00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:46.710
criticize. You get annoyed

00:14:46.720 --> 00:14:48.389
sometimes and your flesh

00:14:48.399 --> 00:14:49.990
goes, 'Man, I wish that was

00:14:49.990 --> 00:14:50.000
mine,'because

00:14:50.000 --> 00:14:51.750
that's

00:14:51.750 --> 00:14:51.760
covetousness.

00:14:51.760 --> 00:14:53.750
But I just go, 'Hey, whatever you have

00:14:53.760 --> 00:14:57.430
for me, Father, bless me in my

00:14:57.430 --> 00:14:57.440
house.'Father,

00:14:57.440 --> 00:14:59.430
you're no

00:14:59.430 --> 00:14:59.440
respecter

00:14:59.440 --> 00:15:01.990
of persons, and what you did

00:15:02.000 --> 00:15:05.350
for them, you'll do for me. So I know,

00:15:05.360 --> 00:15:08.150
God, if I sow into good ground, you said

00:15:08.160 --> 00:15:10.949
that you reap back a 100-fold

00:15:10.949 --> 00:15:10.959
return—some

00:15:10.959 --> 00:15:13.430
30, some 60, and 100-fold. So that's

00:15:13.430 --> 00:15:13.440
what

00:15:13.440 --> 00:15:15.670
I'm trying to tell you all: ask

00:15:15.680 --> 00:15:18.389
God for a creative idea and look at the

00:15:18.399 --> 00:15:20.790
grounds that are blessed.

00:15:20.800 --> 00:15:24.150
Find the blessed 100-fold ground and

00:15:24.150 --> 00:15:24.160
sow

00:15:24.160 --> 00:15:26.550
into it. And I'm telling you, God will

00:15:26.560 --> 00:15:29.509
bless your hands, too. But some people

00:15:29.519 --> 00:15:32.069
keep giving in the same place, same

00:15:32.079 --> 00:15:34.470
time, same everything, and they don't

00:15:34.480 --> 00:15:37.269
ever see. I look at this: if

00:15:37.279 --> 00:15:40.069
you go and visit a church and everybody

00:15:40.079 --> 00:15:43.110
in the congregation is broke,

00:15:44.800 --> 00:15:47.030
check yourself.

00:15:50.639 --> 00:15:54.150
There's a problem if everybody's broke.

00:15:54.160 --> 00:15:56.310
Now, you go into some

00:15:56.310 --> 00:15:56.320
mega-churches

00:15:56.320 --> 00:15:58.150
and there's a lot of

00:15:58.150 --> 00:15:58.160
seeker-friendly

00:15:58.160 --> 00:15:59.910
and their soil is not

00:15:59.920 --> 00:16:01.910
good or whatever. I'm not saying that

00:16:01.920 --> 00:16:03.749
just because you have a rich

00:16:03.759 --> 00:16:05.509
congregation means there's anointing

00:16:05.519 --> 00:16:08.230
there or the hand's favor

00:16:08.230 --> 00:16:08.240
is

00:16:08.240 --> 00:16:10.230
there. Sometimes I go into some

00:16:10.230 --> 00:16:10.240
seeker-friendly

00:16:10.240 --> 00:16:12.389
churches and you go, 'Well, it's

00:16:12.399 --> 00:16:13.749
just because you've got a lot of doctors

00:16:13.759 --> 00:16:15.030
and lawyers here that are just looking

00:16:15.040 --> 00:16:17.189
for something.'But I'm talking about, in

00:16:17.199 --> 00:16:19.590
general, you can feel when the spirit of

00:16:19.590 --> 00:16:19.600
God

00:16:19.600 --> 00:16:21.990
is

00:16:22.000 --> 00:16:23.749
on something. Am I

00:16:23.759 --> 00:16:26.710
making sense? I hope I am because I'm

00:16:26.720 --> 00:16:28.629
trying to teach y'all

00:16:28.639 --> 00:16:31.430
something here—what

00:16:31.430 --> 00:16:31.440
Diana

00:16:31.440 --> 00:16:34.470
and I watch for. Are the

00:16:34.480 --> 00:16:38.069
people blessed? Are

00:16:38.079 --> 00:16:40.389
they spiritually set free? Are they

00:16:40.399 --> 00:16:43.990
being fed the meat of the word so

00:16:44.000 --> 00:16:46.310
that they can stand on the word of God

00:16:46.320 --> 00:16:49.910
when the storms of life come? Or are

00:16:49.920 --> 00:16:52.069
they all busted, their marriage is

00:16:52.079 --> 00:16:53.670
defeated, they're divorced,

00:16:53.680 --> 00:16:55.590
they've got sickness, and their kids are

00:16:55.600 --> 00:16:58.710
run wayward and strung out on drugs,

00:16:58.720 --> 00:17:01.749
sleeping around, and doing bad things? Is

00:17:01.759 --> 00:17:04.470
the congregation successful

00:17:04.480 --> 00:17:06.470
spiritually just as much as they are in

00:17:06.480 --> 00:17:08.230
the natural? That's what I'm trying to

00:17:08.240 --> 00:17:10.390
say. I hope that makes sense.

00:17:12.880 --> 00:17:15.909
I get a lot of flack from

00:17:15.919 --> 00:17:17.669
the emails, and Diana tells me,

00:17:17.679 --> 00:17:19.669
'I want you to address some things

00:17:19.679 --> 00:17:22.069
and tell them where

00:17:22.079 --> 00:17:24.150
we are with that.'And so

00:17:24.160 --> 00:17:27.189
in these videos,

00:17:27.199 --> 00:17:29.669
coming up with content and

00:17:29.679 --> 00:17:32.310
telling you all things, some may be

00:17:32.320 --> 00:17:35.990
a hit and a miss. I'm

00:17:36.000 --> 00:17:38.070
listening and just pressing into Him.

00:17:38.080 --> 00:17:40.310
It's a lot of responsibility. I pray

00:17:40.320 --> 00:17:43.350
y'all have mercy on me. I'm doing

00:17:43.360 --> 00:17:47.190
it. Lord, I just thank You for every

00:17:47.200 --> 00:17:48.710
single person that's representing. He

00:17:48.720 --> 00:17:50.470
said, "I want you to take communion with

00:17:50.480 --> 00:17:53.990
My

00:17:53.990 --> 00:17:54.000
people."I

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:58.630
just had Chipotle chips

00:17:58.630 --> 00:17:58.640
and, Lord,

00:17:58.640 --> 00:18:01.990
we're going to take

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:05.270
communion with Chipotle chips today.

00:18:05.280 --> 00:18:07.110
To God be the glory. It's not

00:18:07.120 --> 00:18:09.750
religious. It's personal. And Jesus

00:18:09.760 --> 00:18:11.750
wants you to be personal with Him. Don't

00:18:11.760 --> 00:18:13.830
get all flaky. People get all

00:18:13.830 --> 00:18:13.840
hyperspiritual

00:18:13.840 --> 00:18:15.190
and you got to have the

00:18:15.200 --> 00:18:16.950
wafer. And that's what I've said before.

00:18:16.960 --> 00:18:18.630
He just looks at the heart. He looks at

00:18:18.640 --> 00:18:20.789
the inward man and He just says,

00:18:20.799 --> 00:18:22.870
"Man, My kid, he loves Me and he wants

00:18:22.880 --> 00:18:25.270
to have fellowship with Me

00:18:25.270 --> 00:18:25.280
today."We

00:18:25.280 --> 00:18:27.110
don't have to go "thee"and "thou."I just

00:18:27.120 --> 00:18:30.870
go, "Jesus, I'm here. I just want to

00:18:30.880 --> 00:18:33.110
have fellowship with You today. Let's

00:18:33.120 --> 00:18:35.590
sit down and

00:18:35.590 --> 00:18:35.600
talk."Do

00:18:35.600 --> 00:18:38.150
you understand? He's wanting to be

00:18:38.160 --> 00:18:40.950
your Father and a friend. He's

00:18:40.960 --> 00:18:43.669
not some God up there saying, "Where have you

00:18:43.679 --> 00:18:45.190
been?"Hey,

00:18:45.200 --> 00:18:48.070
He's there with His daddy arms and

00:18:48.080 --> 00:18:50.310
saying, "Hey, come on in, kids. Let's go

00:18:50.320 --> 00:18:53.510
have some coffee."Do you understand?

00:18:53.520 --> 00:18:55.669
God is a God of ever-present help in a

00:18:55.679 --> 00:18:57.990
time of need. And He wants to be your

00:18:58.000 --> 00:18:59.909
buddy. He wants to be your friend. He

00:18:59.919 --> 00:19:02.470
wants to see that you have

00:19:02.480 --> 00:19:05.110
everything your heart desires and that

00:19:05.120 --> 00:19:07.990
you are fulfilled in every area of your

00:19:08.000 --> 00:19:11.029
life. Above all things, that you prosper

00:19:11.039 --> 00:19:12.710
and be in health even as your soul

00:19:12.720 --> 00:19:16.150
prospers, full of joy.

00:19:16.160 --> 00:19:19.270
I hope that blesses you because

00:19:19.280 --> 00:19:22.630
I'm telling you that's what He wants,

00:19:22.640 --> 00:19:25.430
and a lot of you don't know Him.

00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:29.270
You know about Him, but you don't know

00:19:29.280 --> 00:19:33.110
Him. You know a lot about Him

00:19:33.120 --> 00:19:35.909
and He may know a lot about you, but

00:19:35.909 --> 00:19:35.919
does—and

00:19:35.919 --> 00:19:38.630
He knows you—but does He know you? I

00:19:38.640 --> 00:19:40.950
mean, is He allowed—do you allow Him to

00:19:40.960 --> 00:19:42.950
be in your life? Do you allow Him to be

00:19:42.960 --> 00:19:45.430
Lord over your life? Does that make

00:19:45.440 --> 00:19:47.909
sense? Do you allow Him to be Lord over

00:19:47.919 --> 00:19:51.510
your life? You still keep Him at

00:19:51.520 --> 00:19:54.470
arm's length. "I just have enough, just

00:19:54.480 --> 00:19:57.350
maybe I can just scratch into heaven.

00:19:57.360 --> 00:19:58.950
I just want to scratch my way into

00:19:58.960 --> 00:20:01.350
heaven. I just ride the

00:20:01.360 --> 00:20:03.110
fence."So

00:20:03.120 --> 00:20:05.750
stupid, whenever He wants to have a

00:20:05.760 --> 00:20:07.270
relationship with you and have abundance

00:20:07.280 --> 00:20:09.830
to the full until it overflows. There's a

00:20:09.840 --> 00:20:12.870
helicopter.

00:20:12.880 --> 00:20:14.630
So, Father, we just thank You

00:20:14.640 --> 00:20:16.870
for all our law enforcement as they fly

00:20:16.880 --> 00:20:19.430
by.

00:20:19.440 --> 00:20:21.270
That's medical. Father, whoever's on

00:20:21.280 --> 00:20:22.870
that medical helicopter, we

00:20:22.880 --> 00:20:24.390
thank You, Lord, that You protect that

00:20:24.400 --> 00:20:30.390
family.

00:20:30.400 --> 00:20:31.909
Lord, we thank You that You heal the

00:20:31.919 --> 00:20:33.909
bodies. Everybody that has something,

00:20:33.919 --> 00:20:36.390
God, there's so many needs. There's so

00:20:36.400 --> 00:20:37.909
many people that are broken. There's so

00:20:37.919 --> 00:20:40.470
many people that need more.

00:20:40.480 --> 00:20:41.909
There's so many people that are walking

00:20:41.919 --> 00:20:45.270
in lack in their bodies and health.

00:20:45.280 --> 00:20:46.870
And You said Your words are life to

00:20:46.880 --> 00:20:49.750
those that find them and

00:20:49.760 --> 00:20:52.710
health to all their flesh.

00:20:52.720 --> 00:20:54.710
So, Father, we find Your word today. We

00:20:54.720 --> 00:20:56.789
find You and we thank You, Lord, that

00:20:56.799 --> 00:20:58.630
You said in Your word, by Your stripes,

00:20:58.640 --> 00:21:01.669
we're healed. Now, I

00:21:01.669 --> 00:21:01.679
agree—by

00:21:01.679 --> 00:21:02.950
Your stripes, they're healed. And I just

00:21:02.960 --> 00:21:04.710
pray for every person that's on here

00:21:04.720 --> 00:21:06.870
today. And we call healing and wholeness

00:21:06.880 --> 00:21:08.870
and wellness over them right now in

00:21:08.870 --> 00:21:08.880
Jesus'name.

00:21:08.880 --> 00:21:11.270
And we thank You, Lord,

00:21:11.280 --> 00:21:13.270
that You said that they're healed. And

00:21:13.280 --> 00:21:14.710
Father, we thank You, Lord, that this is

00:21:14.720 --> 00:21:16.549
the meal that heals. And we take this

00:21:16.559 --> 00:21:19.190
body in the name of Jesus. And we lift

00:21:19.190 --> 00:21:19.200
it

00:21:19.200 --> 00:21:20.870
up before You, God. And we thank You that

00:21:20.880 --> 00:21:23.029
You were wounded for our transgressions,

00:21:23.039 --> 00:21:24.950
You were bruised for our iniquities, the

00:21:24.960 --> 00:21:27.270
chastisement of our peace was upon You,

00:21:27.280 --> 00:21:30.549
and with Your stripes, we are healed.

00:21:30.559 --> 00:21:32.149
And we thank You, Lord, for this body

00:21:32.159 --> 00:21:35.430
right now.

00:21:35.440 --> 00:21:40.950
Now, Lord,

00:21:40.960 --> 00:21:54.390
we thank You for the blood.

00:21:54.400 --> 00:21:55.909
Never be in a hurry, Father, to be

00:21:55.919 --> 00:21:58.950
with You.

00:21:58.960 --> 00:22:05.830
Always in a rush.

00:22:05.840 --> 00:22:10.230
People, just be patient and wait on You.

00:22:10.240 --> 00:22:11.830
It's like, what else we have to do in

00:22:11.840 --> 00:22:14.950
life other than to find You?

00:22:14.960 --> 00:22:18.870
All the other stuff doesn't matter.

00:22:18.880 --> 00:22:21.510
Lord, we take the blood of Jesus and we

00:22:21.520 --> 00:22:23.590
apply the blood of Jesus over everything

00:22:23.600 --> 00:22:25.669
we do. We plead the blood of Jesus over

00:22:25.679 --> 00:22:27.990
our families and over our sins

00:22:28.000 --> 00:22:29.830
and over everything, Father. And You

00:22:29.840 --> 00:22:31.990
said if we make much of the blood, the

00:22:32.000 --> 00:22:35.029
blood makes much of us. And we apply the

00:22:35.039 --> 00:22:37.270
blood over our lives today. And we say

00:22:37.280 --> 00:22:39.350
thank You, Father, for the blood. And we

00:22:39.360 --> 00:22:41.430
plead the blood over us, Father. For

00:22:41.440 --> 00:22:43.510
where the blood is applied, Satan cannot

00:22:43.520 --> 00:22:46.149
touch it. And I thank You for the blood

00:22:46.159 --> 00:22:47.909
today, God. I cover my family in the

00:22:47.919 --> 00:22:50.630
blood of Jesus.

00:22:50.640 --> 00:22:55.590
Take the blood

00:22:55.600 --> 00:22:58.310
now. Lord, thank You that You're my

00:22:58.320 --> 00:23:00.870
healer. We're healed

00:23:00.880 --> 00:23:04.549
today.

00:23:04.559 --> 00:23:07.110
Well,

00:23:07.120 --> 00:23:11.110
God is good. And I pray these videos

00:23:11.120 --> 00:23:13.029
are doing something for your spiritual

00:23:13.039 --> 00:23:15.350
walk because I try to get real with

00:23:15.360 --> 00:23:16.870
y'all.

00:23:16.880 --> 00:23:19.909
